rmalcy\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Within that dark period of history, sports gave people that escape, that little window of life while evading the dread of death right outside their homes.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that dark period\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"that little window\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"the dread\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Filipinos, the return of basketball leagues, as expected, provided that reprieve, with little to no expectations of hope coming from other sporting sources.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9999760668701149, \"rank\": 2.391460745744167e-05, \"text\": \"Filipinos\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"basketball leagues\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"that reprieve\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"no expectations\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"other sporting sources\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then seemingly out of nowhere, the Tokyo Olympics, postponed a year due to the life-changing pandemic, gave Filipinos exactly what they wanted: hope, surprisingly at the cost of normalcy.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 771, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.