\": \"the country's most prolific run\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That medal spree alone would have been a cause for historic celebration, but star weightlifterHidilyn Diazdecided to ride the winning wave as well, capping the campaign with an improbablegolden liftthat ended the Philippines' 97-year odyssey for the ever-elusive Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1271, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.998346996366564, \"rank\": 0.0016360143924248687, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That medal spree\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"a cause\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"historic celebration\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"star weightlifterHidilyn\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"the winning wave\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"an improbablegolden liftthat\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the ever-elusive Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With tears streaming down a mask-covered face, Diaz created the country's greatest sporting moment as the Philippine national anthem was played in an Olympic awarding ceremony for the first time in a non-demo sport capacity, making for an indelible memory that Filipinos back home all shared with her.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1442, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lupang_Hinirang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippine national anthem\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lupang_Hinirang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lupang_Hinirang\"}, {\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9999760668701149, \"rank\": 2.391460745744167e-05, \"text\": \"Filipinos\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"a mask-covered face\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"Diaz\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's greatest sporting moment\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic awarding ceremony\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"a non-demo sport capacity\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"an indelible memory\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is now 2024, and while the memories of 2021 are still freshly etched in the minds of all Filipino sports fans, the landscape ahead of the Paris Olympics has shifted considerably.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9996304067541996, \"rank\": 0.0003394345881789962, \"text\": \"Filipino\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the memories\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the minds\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"the landscape\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diaz has all but ridden off into the sunset, now contemplating a quiet family life after being bumped off the women's 59kg qualifiers by none other than her compatriot and fellow Tokyo OlympianElreen Ando.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2001, \"end\": 2006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999274702655971, \"rank\": 7.253499447966574e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Diaz\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"the sunset\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"a quiet family life\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1904}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 59kg qualifiers\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"her compatriot\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UpstartsVanessa SarnoandJohn Ceniza, meanwhile, are set on making the most of their Olympic debuts in Paris, in the women's 71kg and men's 61kg divisions, respectively.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0336090559366882e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"UpstartsVanessa SarnoandJohn Ceniza\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic debuts\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 71kg\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"men's 61kg divisions\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The narratives and pressures have been inevitably set by the icon who came before them, but the soft-spoken trio is nonetheless ready to take on all challenges and accept all outcomes, whether they result in a medal like her or not.\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The narratives\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"pressures\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the icon\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"the soft-spoken trio\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"all challenges\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"all outcomes\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, I do not mind the pressure at all.\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just have a lot of trust in myself that I can get a medal,\\\" Ando said in Filipino.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.883408105251482e-22, \"text\": \"Ando\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All I need to do is improve my lifts.\\\"\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my lifts\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only weightlifter in the Paris contingent who has experienced the intimidating aura of the Olympics, the 25-year-old Ando kept her advice simple for her fellow lifters who are about to step into the sport's biggest stage.\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0336090559366882e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.883408105251482e-22, \"text\": \"Ando\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ando_Masahashi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intimidating aura\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2706}, {\"ngram\": \"her advice\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"her fellow lifters\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's biggest stage\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just have to focus on our attempts and keep faith in ourselves,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our attempts\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ceniza, actually the oldest of the trio at 26 years old, likewise does not have lofty dreams with golden gleams, but rather, he just draws his strength from people who believe in him, particularly his weightlifting idols like Diaz and another former Olympian, Nestor Colonia.\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998603616502, \"rank\": 1.3963014715949312e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3170, \"end\": 3184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nestor_Colonia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nestor Colonia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nestor_Colonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nestor_Colonia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ceniza\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2916}, {\"ngram\": \"the trio\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"lofty dreams\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"golden gleams\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"his strength\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3061}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly his weightlifting idols\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3130}, {\"ngram\": \"Diaz\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all about sacrifice and chasing goals you know you can achieve,\\\" he said in Filipino.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sacrifice\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"goals\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It also helps that you have idols in weightlifting like Nestor, who has kept on pushing me and telling me I will get to Paris as long as I put in the work and the sacrifices.\\\"\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3336, \"end\": 3342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Nestor\", \"score\": 0.9995053944877902, \"rank\": 0.0004365020551627635, \"text\": \"Nestor\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Nestor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Nestor\"}, {\"begin\": 3400, \"end\": 3405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0336090559366882e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"idols\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifices\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same goes for the 20-year-old Sarno, who credits her own sturdy support system in building her confidence for her impending Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3491, \"end\": 3496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"score\": 0.9999999991564437, \"rank\": 8.436430662991935e-10, \"text\": \"Sarno\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarno\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own sturdy support system\", \"from\": 3510, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"her confidence\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"her impending Olympic debut\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ever since I started weightlifting, my parents have been very supportive and always all-out for me, starting from the local competition levels,\\\" she said in Filipino.\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"the local competition levels\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3744}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Heading to Paris, all we wish for is we stay injury-free, and apply what we have learned in training - the little things to help us improve our personal records.\\\"\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3782, \"end\": 3787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0336090559366882e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3871}, {\"ngram\": \"the little things\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"our per